like, "I know everything.

00:56:46.560 --> 00:56:47.920
You are just going to sit there

00:56:47.920 --> 00:56:49.220
and you're going
to listen to me."

00:56:49.220 --> 00:56:50.520
And even if you've been
taught to sort of like,

00:56:50.520 --> 00:56:51.820
"I'm going to run a seminar."

00:56:51.820 --> 00:56:53.120
It's totally a fake seminar.

00:56:53.120 --> 00:56:55.870
In which you are guiding
the discussion, to an answer

00:56:55.870 --> 00:56:58.210
