01:04:21.210 --> 01:04:24.700
&gt;&gt; But do, but do
people thank the-- never!

01:04:24.700 --> 01:04:27.770
&gt;&gt; I thank you by
name in my book.

01:04:27.770 --> 01:04:29.770
&gt;&gt; You and all the, all
the central library staff

01:04:29.770 --> 01:04:31.070
in the Folger.

01:04:31.070 --> 01:04:32.370
Look it up.

01:04:32.370 --> 01:04:33.670
