01:04:56.300 --> 01:05:00.250
In which we think of that
as being a male field.

01:05:00.250 --> 01:05:01.550
But nobody, nobody.

01:05:01.550 --> 01:05:04.570
You look, you look to
see digital images,

01:05:04.570 --> 01:05:07.030
digital facsimiles of books.

01:05:07.030 --> 01:05:08.680
We're going to talk about this
