01:05:37.820 --> 01:05:41.960
Very, like super-carefully
professionally carefully

01:05:41.960 --> 01:05:45.410
slowly done.

01:05:45.410 --> 01:05:49.300
You might know the name
of the head of that lab.

01:05:49.300 --> 01:05:50.610
