always know the names

01:06:31.040 --> 01:06:32.340
underneath it.

01:06:32.340 --> 01:06:36.000
But is the process sort
of tracing that through.

01:06:36.000 --> 01:06:39.340
Just like those, so
I've got two answers.

01:06:39.340 --> 01:06:41.350
Just like any compositor.

