Is the thing that
drives me nuts.

01:07:22.300 --> 01:07:24.540
They're just inherently
fabulous people who understand,

01:07:24.540 --> 01:07:26.040
who are always on the
right side of history.

01:07:26.040 --> 01:07:27.390
Which is of course idiotic.

01:07:27.390 --> 01:07:29.580
Because we're just people.

