be acknowledged.

01:07:37.320 --> 01:07:38.800
And it can either
be acknowledged

01:07:38.800 --> 01:07:42.180
through decent money.

01:07:42.180 --> 01:07:44.530
Or you can get credit
to your name.

01:07:44.530 --> 01:07:46.970
We don't have the money.

